data.description: Coming soon*9/14* This Beauty is nestled in a desirable Hazelwood neighborhood offering the perfect blend of style, comfort, and functionality. With 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms spread across 1,887 square feet of living space, the home provides ample space for you and your loved ones to create lasting memories. As you step inside, you'll be captivated by the seamless flow and layout that maximizes both privacy and connectivity. The open-concept living area is flooded with natural light, creating an inviting ambiance for relaxation and entertainment. Retreat to the spacious master bedroom that features its own ensuite bathroom for added convenience. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms provide ample space for family or guest. The open flowing lower level can be transformed into a home offices, hobby rooms or a phenomenal entertaining area that suits your needs. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make 698 Carriage Lane your new home. Schedule your private showing today!
